{"tid":235744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得入境事務處應該比返OT錢比呢位連登巴打","createTime":"2017-05-09T08:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T08:45:50.000Z","uid":30807,"like":92,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"40accaae9d806eef0b7eee59d8f037d1df78180c","tid":235744,"uid":30807,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:38:42.000Z","msg":"事源：<br />\n人見人愛#103127於一個月前有志加入入境處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QU69X98.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQU69X98.png&h=50c80ccf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個月後就係入境處拉HA既POST度盡心盡忠盡力聲討HA <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/235367/page/13\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/235367/page/13</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iAeW984.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiAeW984.png&h=8b4fc181&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mU9EV19.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmU9EV19.png&h=3efc1426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8677D3A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8677D3A.png&h=130acc1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢位巴打講既野都相當有道理，大家唔好因為佢打簡體字就廢佢言<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xjJD24e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxjJD24e.png&h=feacf535&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋亦有相當理性既一面，泛民支持者都應該支持佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m60E0Pu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm60E0Pu.png&h=f9bfae55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n回歸正題：<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打可以幫我地關注下在家工作OT無補水既情況??<br />\n<br />\n休班代老闆發短訊裁定OT<br />\n台灣昨公布首宗員工下班後收到僱主短訊辦公事而獲賠加班費的案例，涉事的電子廠員工早前被遣散後，向僱主追討賠償時，提出在非上班時間經常收到僱主的公事短訊，仲裁委員會審閱通訊紀錄資料後，認為事主確實「加班」一千三百多分鐘，裁決可獲兩千五百九十八元新台幣（下同，約六百四十港元）加班費。是次案例引起輿論討論，商界普遍表示不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170312/00178_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170312%2F00178_001.html&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=74e30d47\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170312/00178_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd3cfe727f35c29c9548b1cf0192defd5d5d1ee","tid":235744,"uid":93900,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:40:33.000Z","msg":"又嚟文革<br />\n咁只會令人愈嚟愈憎ha"},{"pid":"8d8dbdc62c1ac6555b97bc58b7ee1ade3346c703","tid":235744,"uid":30807,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:42:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又嚟文革<br />\n咁只會令人愈嚟愈憎ha</blockquote><br />\n巴打岩，質疑人地既出身就話人講野冇說服力真係好文革<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oAQ0Cph.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoAQ0Cph.png&h=9be55630&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ea58de170cff10ba5fa6cd68392c769397e9151","tid":235744,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:43:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又嚟文革<br />\n咁只會令人愈嚟愈憎ha</blockquote><br />\nagger,普通會員仔發個言都要去起底批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff010cc48456abae904578462cbc5d624bd11a89","tid":23574